Problem:
Create a program to manage student records for a school.

Requirements:
1. Add new student records(name, roll and grades)
2. Update student records
3.Delete record
4. Search record via roll or name
5. save data and load when program starts


planning:
1. to add new student record have to take user input .
2. to update the data will save the data as a text file.
3.roll ar name er format specific rakhbo jate search korar kaj complicated na hoy
4.to delete a student record search them by their roll number and remove the student from records.
5.we can search for students by their roll number for more exact match.
6.save all student records as a text file.
7.Have to retrieve all the data when the program restarts
































































